videos.description: Joseph Girard III gets the steal, and Cole Swider knocks down the long-range 3-pointer to extend the Orange's lead.

videos.description: Syracuse's Buddy Boeheim's second effort pays off as he muscles his way to the basket and gets the layup to fall.
